Parameters

Item
Type: SystemInt32
This is an integer between 1 and 9, inclusive, indicating the preference item considered.
  1. Multi-response case design
  2. Phi (Structural Steel)
  3. Phi (Structural Steel Fracture)
  4. Phi (Concrete)
  5. Phi (Reinforcement)
  6. HSS welding type
  7. Reduce HSS thickness
  8. Pattern live load factor
  9. Demand/capacity ratio limit
Value
Type: SystemDouble
The value of the considered preference item.
  1. Multi-response case design
    • 1 - Envelopes
    • 2 - Step-by-step
    • 3 - Last step
    • 4 - Envelopes -- All
    • 5 - Step-by-step -- All
  2. Phi (Structural Steel)

    Value > 0

  3. Phi (Structural Steel Fracture)

    Value > 0

  4. Phi (Concrete)

    Value > 0

  5. Phi (Reinforcement)

    Value > 0

  6. HSS welding type
    • 1 - ERW
    • 2 - SAW
  7. Reduce HSS thickness

    0 = No

    Any other value = Yes

  8. Pattern live load factor

    Value > 0

  9. Demand/capacity ratio limit

    Value > 0

Return Value

Type: Int32
Returns zero if the item is successfully set; otherwise it returns a nonzero value.

Examples
VB
Copy
Public Sub Example()
   Dim SapModel As cSapModel
   Dim EtabsObject As cOAPI
   Dim ret As Integer = -1
   Dim Value As Double
   Dim ProgDet As Boolean

'create ETABS object
   Dim myHelper as cHelper = New Helper
   EtabsObject = myHelper.CreateObjectProgID("CSI.ETABS.API.ETABSObject")

'start ETABS application
  ret = EtabsObject.ApplicationStart()

'create SapModel object
   SapModel = EtabsObject.SapModel

'initialize model
   ret = SapModel.InitializeNewModel()

'create steel deck template model
   ret = SapModel.File.NewSteelDeck(4, 12, 12, 4, 4, 24, 24)

'set composite column design code
   ret = SapModel.DesignCompositeColumn.SetCode("CSA S16-19")

'set overwrite item
   ret = SapModel.DesignCompositeColumn.CSAS16_19.SetPreference(2, 1)

'close ETABS
   EtabsObject.ApplicationExit(False)

'clean up variables
   SapModel = Nothing
   EtabsObject = Nothing

End Sub
